                {
                    "id": "turbulence_full_deformation",
                    "description": "Smagorinsky turbulence closure driven by a full deformation tensor (turbulence D11=0.001, D22=−0.001, D33=0, D12=0.005, D13=0.003, D23=0.002 s^-1, Δ_grid=600 m): the total deformation |Def| (Eq. 2.18), the eddy viscosity K_M = (k·Δ)^2·|Def| (Eq. 2.17) and the turbulent heat diffusivity K_H = K_M (Eq. 2.19). Mirrors the standalone smagorinsky.esm `full_deformation` test.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {
                        "Clark1977AnelasticSystem.turbulence.D11": 0.001,
